            [day_title] => Arrival and Hotel Check-in in Lubumbashi
            [day_description] => Upon arrival in Lubumbashi, guests are transferred to their hotel to rest after their flight. A briefing session about the tour’s schedule follows, and depending on the flight arrival time, a short walk or transportation can be arranged to explore the area.
