        (
            [day_number] => 2
            [day_title] => Afternoon
            [day_description] => After the trek, you will return to the park headquarters for a well-deserved lunch at a trusted local lodge. For those interested, the afternoon offers an optional visit to the Iby’Iwacu Cultural Village. Here you can engage directly with local communities, experience traditional Rwandan culture, and learn about the important role community-based tourism plays in supporting conservation and livelihoods. This cultural visit strengthens the connection between tourism and sustainable development, giving you a fuller appreciation of the region’s heritage.
        )

